<div class="modal-header">
    <button type="button" id="find_close" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
    <h4 class="modal-title">아이디/비밀번호 찾기</h4>
</div>
<div class="modal-body">
    <div class="main-content">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="row">
                <div>
                    <form class="container-fluid" id="findIdForm">
                        <div class="panel">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                <div class="row form-group">
                                    <div class="col-md-2">
                                        <a>이메일 *</a>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-10">
                                        <input id="findid_email" name="findid_email" type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="담당자 이메일">
                                        <small class="invalid-feedback text-danger" id="findid_email_feedback"></small>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row form-group pull-right">
                                    <div class="col-md-4">
                                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" onclick="javascript:findId()">아이디 찾기</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="clearfix"></div> 
                                <div class="alert alert-info" role="alert">
                                    <i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i> 담당자의 이메일을 입력하시면 아이디가 메일로 발송됩니다.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                    <form class="container-fluid" id="findPwdForm">
                        <div class="panel">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                <div class="row form-group">
                                    <div class="col-md-2">
                                        <a>ID *</a>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-10">
                                        <input id="findpwd_id" name="findpwd_id" type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="사용자 ID">
                                        <small class="invalid-feedback text-danger" id="findpwd_id_feedback"></small>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row form-group">
                                    <div class="col-md-2">
                                        <a>이메일 *</a>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-10">
                                        <input id="findpwd_email" name="findpwd_email" type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="담당자 이메일">
                                        <small class="invalid-feedback text-danger" id="findpwd_email_feedback"></small>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row form-group pull-right">
                                    <div class="col-md-4">
                                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" onclick="javascript:findPwd()">비밀번호 찾기</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="clearfix"></div> 
                                <div class="alert alert-info" role="alert">
                                    <i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i> 가입하신 아이디와 담당자의 메일 주소를 입력하시면 비밀번호가 초기화 되어 메일로 발송 됩니다.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>        
</div>
